# M2.12: allow `.github/workflows/` to be committed. The previous
# blanket `.github` ignore was a cleanup-era over-broad rule; the
# CI workflow file lives here and is required for M2.12 (MCP smoke
# gate). Other `.github/` artifacts (dependabot, codeowners, etc.)
# remain fine to add — this entry is removed, not narrowed.
.junie/
.windsurfrules
.playwright-cli/
nexus-wasm-complete-pack.xml

